Welcome to AHKontroller (With XInput) - JoyToMinecraft Release!
This is a Release Branch with just JoyToMinecraft and its libraries.

Completly new to AutoHotkey?
1. Install AutoHotkey (Must support version 2)
2. Run joytoMinecraft.ahk with AutoHotkey
3. Press F10 or the XBox Button to exit after you're done!

JoyToMinecraft (JTMC) v1.3 features:
*  Type: KeyboardKey(ControllerKey)
*  Movement: WASD(Left Stick) Space(A) R(X) Sprint(Click Left Stick) {SNEAKING IS CHANGED TO X.}
*  Camera: Mouse(Right Stick), Slow(Hold down Right Stick)
*  Inventory: E(Y)
*  Throw: Q(Button Left of Xbox)
*  Slot Switching: 123456789(L/R Shoulder (or Bumper))
*  Actions: MouseLClick(Right Trigger) MouseRClick(Left Trigger)
*  Menu: Escape(Button Right of Xbox)
*  Stop Script: (XBox Button)
* 
* Not Yet Implemented:
* Better Shifting, Offhand (Not on 1.8), InvSlot(DPad)
* Cheats: Autoclick, KeepHolding, LootAll

